<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
<head>
    <title>認証成功</title>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@tailwindcss/browser@4"></script>
</head>
<body class="bg-gray-50">
    <div class="min-h-[calc(100vh-1rem)] lg:min-h-[calc(100vh-4rem)] flex flex-col max-w-4xl mx-auto p-4">
        <article class="flex-1">
            <header class="text-center py-8">
                <h1 class="text-3xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">認証成功</h1>
                <div class="border-b border-gray-300 w-full"></div>
            </header>
            
            <section class="py-8">
                <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm border p-6 lg:p-8">
                    <div class="text-center space-y-6">
                        <div class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto bg-green-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
                            <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-green-600 rounded-full"></div>
                        </div>
                        <h2 class="text-2xl lg:text-3xl font-semibold text-green-600">認証に成功しました</h2>
                        
                        <div class="bg-green-50 border border-green-200 rounded-lg p-6 text-left space-y-4">
                            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-green-800">次の手順</h3>
                            <p class="text-green-800 lg:text-lg leading-relaxed">
                                再びそのまま書き込みを行うか、メール欄に以下のトークンを貼り付けてください（一部のブラウザでは貼り付けなくても書けます）
                            </p>
                        </div>
                        
                        <div class="space-y-4">
                            <div class="text-left">
                                <label for="token-input" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-900 mb-2">認証トークン</label>
                                <div class="relative">
                                    <input 
                                        type="text" 
                                        id="token-input"
                                        value="#{{token}}" 
                                        onfocus="this.select();" 
                                        readonly
                                        class="w-full px-4 py-3 text-sm lg:text-base border border-gray-300 rounded-lg bg-gray-50 font-mono text-center focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 focus:border-blue-500"
                                    >
                                    <button 
                                        onclick="navigator.clipboard.writeText(document.getElementById('token-input').value); this.textContent='コピー済み!'; setTimeout(() => this.textContent='コピー', 2000);"
                                        class="absolute right-2 top-1/2 transform -translate-y-1/2 bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white text-xs px-3 py-1 rounded transition duration-200"
                                    >
                                        コピー
                                    </button>
                                </div>
                                <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mt-2">
                                    ※ #以降の内容は書き込み時に自動的に消去されます
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        
                        <div class="pt-6 space-y-3">
                            <a href="/" class="inline-block bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white font-semibold py-3 px-6 rounded-lg transition duration-200 lg:text-lg">
                                トップページに戻る
                            </a>
                            <br>
                            <button onclick="window.close()" class="inline-block text-gray-600 hover:text-gray-800 font-medium lg:text-lg underline">
                                このページを閉じる
                            </button>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>
        </article>
        
        <footer class="py-6 text-center mt-8">
            <p class="text-xs text-gray-400">
                This BBS is powered by 
                <a href="https://github.com/edginer/eddist" class="text-gray-500 hover:text-gray-700 underline">
                    Eddist
                </a>
            </p>
        </footer>
    </div>
</body>
</html>